<%- include('navbar.ejs') %>

<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/student/privacy.css">

<!-- Page Header (same as event page) -->
<section class="page-header" style="background-image: url('/images/background image.jpg');">
    <div class="container">
        <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="lead fw-bold">How we collect, use, and protect your information</p>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Privacy Content -->
<section class="privacy-section py-5">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="privacy-card">
            <div class="privacy-date">
                <i class="fas fa-calendar-alt me-2"></i> Last updated: April 2, 2025
            </div>

            <div class="privacy-block">
                <h3><i class="fas fa-info-circle me-2"></i> Introduction</h3>
                <p>Welcome to the Department of Electronics and Computer Engineering Event Portal. Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you use our website, including all related pages, features, and content.</p>
                <p>By accessing or using our portal, you agree to the terms of this Privacy Policy. If you do not agree, please do not use our services.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="privacy-block">
                <h3><i class="fas fa-database me-2"></i> Information We Collect</h3>
                <p>We may collect the following types of information:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Personal Information:</strong> Name, email address, department, year of study, phone number (when you register for events or contact us).</li>
                    <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Pages visited, time spent, event registrations, login activity.</li>
                    <li><strong>Device Information:</strong> IP address, browser type, operating system.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="privacy-block">
                <h3><i class="fas fa-chart-line me-2"></i> How We Use Your Information</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>To process event registrations and manage attendance.</li>
                    <li>To send event reminders, updates, and approval status.</li>
                    <li>To improve our website and user experience.</li>
                    <li>To generate analytics (e.g., participation trends).</li>
                    <li>To respond to inquiries and support requests.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="privacy-block">
                <h3><i class="fas fa-shield-alt me-2"></i> Data Security</h3>
                <p>We implement industry-standard security measures (encryption, secure servers, access controls) to protect your personal information. However, no method of transmission over the internet is 100% secure. We cannot guarantee absolute security.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="privacy-block">
                <h3><i class="fas fa-cookie-bite me-2"></i> Cookies & Tracking</h3>
                <p>We use cookies to enhance your browsing experience. Cookies are small text files stored on your device. You may disable cookies in your browser settings, but some portal features may not function properly.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="privacy-block">
                <h3><i class="fas fa-share-alt me-2"></i> Third-Party Links</h3>
                <p>Our portal may contain links to external sites (e.g., social media, Google Maps). We are not responsible for the privacy practices of those websites. Please review their policies before providing any information.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="privacy-block">
                <h3><i class="fas fa-child me-2"></i> Children's Privacy</h3>
                <p>Our services are intended for college students and faculty. We do not knowingly collect information from individuals under 13 years of age.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="privacy-block">
                <h3><i class="fas fa-sync-alt me-2"></i> Changes to This Policy</h3>
                <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with a revised "Last updated" date. Continued use of the portal constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="privacy-block">
                <h3><i class="fas fa-envelope me-2"></i> Contact Us</h3>
                <p>If you have questions about this Privacy Policy or your data, please contact us:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Email: <a href="mailto:principal.parikramaengg@gmail.com">principal.parikramaengg@gmail.com</a></li>
                    <li>Phone: +91 94031 90505</li>
                    <li>Address: Faculty of Engineering, Kashti, Shrigonda, Ahilyanagar, Maharashtra – 414701</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="privacy-block text-center mt-4">
                <a href="/" class="btn btn-outline-primary rounded-pill px-4">← Back to Home</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

